        <h5 class="text-danger mt-3"><b>About ASEAN-India Network of Universities</b></h5>
        <p class="mt-3" style="text-align: justify;">
	<span style="font-size: 21px;">ASEAN-India Network of Universities (AINU) is envisioned as the knowledge ecosystem forged
	through the linkages among the premier institutions and universities in India and ASEAN Member States with
	Nalanda University as the nodal institution. The initiative is invested in framing and
	strengthening the paradigms of knowledge production in order to engage with region-specific
        concerns.This collaboration will ensure capacity building and creation of regional thought leaders from the Asia- Pacific in the emerging multi-polar world.
        </span></p>
        <div class="col-sm-2">
            
        </div>
    </div>
