                    <div class="col-sm-8">
                        <p style="font-size: 19px; text-align: justify">
				Hon'ble Prime Minister of India announced at ASEAN-India Commemorative Summit in New
				Delhi in January 2018 about setting up of a network of universities to encourage greater inter-university exchanges between India and ASEAN. The Government of India has designated the
				Nalanda University, Rajgir, to take the lead on the formation, as well as, sustenance of the AINU.
				Keeping in mind the goals of mutual assistance, sustainable progress and equitable development,
				the AINU has been envisaged as a collective knowledge network.
			</p>
